3/rich-the-kid-the-rich-forever-way-release-date/ |title=Rich The Kid Announces 'The Rich Forever Way' Release Date \u2013 XXL |publisher=Xxlmag.com |date= |accessdate=2017-06-04}}</ref>\n* Label: Rich Forever Music\n* Format: Download\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Rich Forever 3]]'' <br />{{small|(with Rich Forever Music)}}\n|\n* Released: June 16, 2017\n* Label: Rich Forever Music, 300 Entertainment\n* Format: Download\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Rich Forever 4'' <br />{{small|(with Rich Forever Music)}}\n|\n* Released: August 2, 2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hiphopdx.com/news/id.52356/title.rich-the-kid-shares-rich-forever-4-project|title=Rich The Kid Shares \"Rich Forever 4\" Project|last=https://hiphopdx.com|first=HipHopDX-|date=2019-08-01|website=HipHopDX|access-date=2019-08-02}}</ref>\n* Label: Rich Forever Music, 300 Entertainment\n* Format: Download, streaming\n|}\n\n===Singles===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of singles as lead artist, with selected chart positions and certifications, showing year released and album name\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:12em;\"| [[List of music recording certifications|Certifications]]\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Billboard Hot 100|US]]<br/><ref name=\"US100\">{{cite web |title=Famous Dex Chart History: Hot 100 |url=https://www.billboard.com/music/famous-dex/chart-history/hot-100 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |accessdate=April 3, 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs|US<br/>R&B/HH]]<br/><ref>{{cite web |title=Famous Dex Chart History: R&B/Hip-Hop Songs |url=https://www.billboard.com/music/famous-dex/chart-history/r-b-hip-hop-songs |work=Billboard |accessdate=April 3, 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col